129.2282-breadth-first-traversing-in-a-g.source:
from collections import deque
def breadth_first(start, f):
    seen = set()
    q = deque([start])
    while q:
        vertex = q.popleft()
        f(vertex)
        seen.add(vertex)
        q.extend(v for v in vertex.adjacent if v not in seen)

130.2283-depth-first-traversing-in-a-gra.source:
def depth_first(start, f):
    seen = set()
    stack = [start]
    while stack:
        vertex = stack.pop()
        f(vertex)
        seen.add(vertex)
        stack.extend(v for v in vertex.adjacent if v not in seen)
